Job Description
Share
We are looking for an European Director of
Food Beverage with a passion for quality and excellence for 5* hotel with
449 rooms and a large F&B; operations with 11 outlets and banquet facilities.
The Director of Food & Beverage, assess,
evaluate and ensure that long and short term goals of all Food & Beverage
operations are met. To direct and manage all food & beverage activities to
maximize food & beverage revenue, profitability and quality goals by
developing and executing marketing strategies, up-selling strategies,
controlling costs, and by providing quality service and products to guests.
All work will be in line with the hotel's guidelines and business plan, and
Hotel (Dusit) corporate guidelines and service concepts.
DOFB will be constantly questioning the
status quo of the Food & Beverage Department's 11 Outlets in coordination
with Executive Chef. Insuring that the latest F&B; trends are applied and
implemented in terms of Food, Beverage, Service, Facilities, Menus Hard and
Soft ware, in addition of coming up with creative Ideas for the division.
Desired Candidate Profile
Qualification:-
* Experience of multi-cultural environments mandatory
* Previous experience in Middle East preferred and Egypt would be a plus
* Far East experience is a plus
* Requires experience in world-class hotels
* Solid experience in F&B; marketing and promotional plans
* Full knowledge of international cuisines
* Strong Leadership and Developer skills
* Experience in developing, implementing and ensuring the success of new concept
* Hands-on professional attitude
* Committed to delivering high levels of customer service
* Strong financial skills and forecasting
* Drive for continuous improvement
* People and target orientated
* Positive attitude and Good communication skills
